Description:
Some Fixes for Mint-X-gtk2-theme (by me). This is themes based on Mint-X from LinuxMint Releases.
Included gtk3 w/o diff. Only edited gtk2-theme.

Based on:
- mint-themes_1.2.8_all
- mint-themes-gtk3_3.8-9_all

Sources, original gtk-theme(s):
2 -> http://packages.linuxmint.com/pool/main/m/mint-themes/
3 -> http://packages.linuxmint.com/pool/main/m/mint-themes-gtk3/


Changelog:

17 -> 17QF
